\u00ed es exactamente donde entra el disruptor.\n\n$NU lo aplic\u00f3 desde afuera: tom\u00f3 los segmentos que los bancos descartaron y subi\u00f3 con un modelo de negocio que ten\u00eda un punto de equilibrio inferior al de los incumbentes.\n\n$MELI lo aplic\u00f3 desde adentro: construy\u00f3 las capas que su propio negocio depend\u00eda: pagos, log\u00edstica, cr\u00e9dito, antes de que otro las capturara. Mercado Pago hoy procesa pagos para millones de usuarios que jam\u00e1s compraron en $MELI.\n\nMismo framework. Posiciones opuestas. Los dos estan ganando.", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "retweetCount": 3, "replyCount": 2, "likeCount": 39, "quoteCount": 1, "viewCount": 3000, "createdAt": "Tue May 05 11:49:03 +0000 2026", "lang": "es", "bookmarkCount": 17, "isReply": false, "inReplyToId": null, "conversationId": "2051630249494949940", "displayTextRange": [0, 274], "inReplyToUserId": null, "inReplyToUsername": null, "author": {"type": "user", "userName": "FedexSTi", "url": "https://x.com/FedexSTi", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/FedexSTi", "id": "2979685073", "name": "Fede Sandler", "isVerified": false, "isBlueVerified": true, "verifiedType": null, "profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2007552004214673408/RLWjc02F_normal.jpg", "coverPicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/2979685073/1767473100", "description": "", "location": "Buenos Aires, Argentina", "followers": 24999, "following": 1622, "status": "", "canDm": true, "canMediaTag": true, "createdAt": "Thu Jan 15 12:40:17 +0000 2015", "entities": {"description": {"urls": []}, "url": {}}, "fastFollowersCount": 0, "favouritesCount": 34946, "hasCustomTimelines": true, "isTranslator": false, "mediaCount": 3457, "statusesCount": 27255, "withheldInCountries": [], "affiliatesHighlightedLabel": {}, "possiblySensitive": false, "pinnedTweetIds": ["1830954015946858889"], "profile_bio": {"description": "Ex-IRO @MercadoLibre & @Nubank. LatAm fintech, capital markets & AI @neuramedia \u00b7 